{"tid":871307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"異議記者失蹤疑雲未解 德國不向沙國輸出軍火","createTime":"2018-10-21T23:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T11:10:30.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"482cb377bfcf4fd9559d919e1992674a6c4c6a28","tid":871307,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T23:23:10.000Z","msg":"異議記者失蹤疑雲未解 德國不向沙國輸出軍火<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3435044\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.udn.com%2Fmoney%2Fstory%2F5599%2F3435044&d=RLcLEq4rWdBVigYxFuaZEkzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=94927f79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/3435044</a><br />\n<br />\n德國總理梅克爾（Angela Merkel）今天表示，在沙烏地阿拉伯異議記者哈紹吉（Jamal Khashoggi）失蹤案未釐清的情況下，德國不會向沙國輸出軍火。<br />\n<br />\n為自家政黨在地方選舉中造勢時，梅克爾再次譴責哈紹吉遭到殺害一案。沙國已坦承，哈紹吉在沙國駐伊斯坦堡領事館遇害。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">梅克爾表示：「首先，對於行凶，我們予以最強烈的譴責。其次，必須儘快讓真相大白─有關釐清案情和懲處行凶者，我們目前遠遠不及&hellip;在此情況下，不會進行軍火的輸出。」</span><br />\n<br />\n（譯者：嚴思祺）"},{"pid":"3fed61b0fe05dbe4d73ba3651c2b51258fbac902","tid":871307,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}